[32m+[m[32m## Installation & Setup[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### 1. Clone Repository[m
 ```bash[m
[32m+[m[32mgit clone https://github.com/anilakbay/ForgeFolio.git[m
 cd ForgeFolio[m
 ```[m
 [m
[31m-3. Bağımlılıkları yükleyin:[m
[32m+[m[32m### 2. Restore Dependencies[m
 ```bash[m
 dotnet restore[m
 ```[m
 [m
[31m-4. Veritabanı bağlantı dizesini `appsettings.json` dosyasında güncelleyin[m
[32m+[m[32m### 3. Database Configuration[m
[32m+[m[32mUpdate connection string in `appsettings.json`:[m
[32m+[m[32m```json[m
[32m+[m[32m{[m
[32m+[m[32m  "ConnectionStrings": {[m
[32m+[m[32m    "DefaultConnection": "Server=(localdb)\\mssqllocaldb;Database=ForgeFolioDB;Trusted_Connection=true;"[m
[32m+[m[32m  }[m
[32m+[m[32m}[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
 [m
[31m-5. Migration'ları çalıştırın:[m
[32m+[m[32m### 4. Database Migration[m
 ```bash[m
 dotnet ef database update[m
 ```[m
 [m
[31m-6. Projeyi çalıştırın:[m
[32m+[m[32m### 5. Launch Application[m
 ```bash[m
 dotnet run[m
 ```[m
